\
## How to Run\
\
1. Install MySQL (or use XAMPP / MySQL Workbench)\
2. Open MySQL Workbench or any SQL client\
3. Open `schema_and_queries.sql`\
4. Run the full script \'97 it creates the database, all tables, inserts data, \
   and executes all queries automatically\
5. Alternatively, import `database_dump.sql` for the pre-populated database\
